# Feature: Flyway Seed Data

## User Story

As a system,
I want initial client data,
so that client-related use cases can be validated and tested.

---

## Tasks

### 1. Create Migration Script

Create file:

src/main/resources/db/migration/V4\_\_seed_clients.sql

---

### 2. Insert Sample Data

Insert sample clients with fields:

- id
- name
- gender
- age
- identification
- address
- phone
- status

---

### 3. Ensure Data Consistency

- IDs must be unique
- Identification must be unique
- Status must be valid (true/false)

---

